Allá,

00:38:18.550 --> 00:38:19.320
Te haré

00:38:19.320 --> 00:38:20.590
Mi emperatriz, solo mía.

00:38:20.590 --> 00:38:21.150
¿Bueno?

00:38:21.630 --> 00:38:22.360
Sigue soñando.

00:38:26.510 --> 00:38:27.480
